                                                            <p class="mb-2 mt-4"><b>1. Introduction</b></p>
                                                            <p class="mb-2">This Cookie Policy ("Policy") underscores our dedication to transparency regarding the utilization of your information. In the pursuit of clarity, we endeavour to expound upon the specifics of how and when we employ cookies on our Websites. It is imperative to note that this policy extends to any Desi Rishta product or service that is linked to or integrates this policy by reference.</p>

                                                            <p class="mb-2 mt-4"><b>2. Does Desi Rishta make use of cookies?</b></p>
                                                            <p class="mb-2"> Desi Rishta employs cookies, tags, and other technologies whenever you interact with any of our websites, mobile sites, or mobile apps (collectively referred to as "the services"). These tools are utilized to ensure the optimal experience for all users and to enhance the security of your account. By continuing to use our services, you agree to the use of cookies and similar technologies for the purposes outlined in this policy. If you prefer not to receive cookies or web beacons, you can choose to stop using our site or adjust your browsing and third-party cookie settings as described below.</p>

                                                            <p class="mb-2 mt-4"><b>3. What precisely does the term "Cookie" refer to?</b></p>
                                                            <p class="mb-2">Cookies are small text pieces stored by a website you visit on your browser and then sent by your web browser with every request to that website. These text files are stored in your web browser, allowing the website or a third party to recognize you and facilitate your next visit, making the website more useful. Essentially, cookies act as a user's ID card for the Desi Rishta servers, enabling us to serve you better and more efficiently, and personalize your experience on our site. Additionally, web beacons, tags, and scripts may be employed on our websites or in emails to assist in delivering cookies, tracking visits, understanding usage and campaign effectiveness, and determining if an email has been opened and acted upon. We may analyse or perform analysis using these technologies and generate reports on an individual and aggregated basis.</p>
                                                            <p class="mb-2"> Cookies can be classified as "persistent" or "session" cookies. Persistent cookies help us recognize you as an existing user, making it easier to return to Desi Rishta or interact with our services without signing in again. Once you sign in, a persistent cookie remains in your browser and will be read by Desi Rishta when you return to one of our sites or a partner site that uses our services. Session cookies, on the other hand, only last for the duration of the session (typically the current visit to a website or a browser session).</p>

                                                            <p class="mb-2 mt-4"><b>4. What roles do cookies play?</b></p>
                                                            <p class="mb-2">When you explore our Websites, we might set up various cookies in your browser, known as First Party Cookies. These cookies are essential for retaining session data while you navigate from one page to another within the website. For example, on our websites, we utilize cookies to comprehend visitor and user preferences, enhance their browsing experience, and analyse usage, navigation, and other statistical data. Additionally, cookies empower us to deliver tailored advertising to you, both within and beyond the Desi Rishta site, and introduce customized features. You have the option to manage cookie usage at the individual browser level. If you opt not to enable cookies or disable them later on, you can still access our Websites, although some features or sections may be limited.</p>
                                                            <p class="mb-2">We may utilize any of the following cookie categories on the Websites, outlined below. Each cookie fits into one of the four following categories:</p>
                                                            <ul class="alpha">
                                                                <li>Necessary Cookies - Essential cookies (First Party Cookies) are sometimes termed "strictly necessary" because they are indispensable for providing many of the services you rely on within the Website. For instance, essential cookies play a crucial role in remembering your preferences while you navigate the Website. They also ensure that you remain logged in to a website. Without these cookies, the login functionality would be rendered inoperative.</li>
                                                                <li>Tracking Cookies - These cookies monitor information about visits to the Desi Rishta and partner websites, enabling us to enhance our performance and make improvements. For instance, they analyse visitor and user behaviour to deliver more pertinent content or recommend specific activities. These cookies gather data on how visitors utilize the Websites, including which site the user originated from, the frequency of each user's visits, and the duration of their stay on the Websites. Additionally, we may utilize analytics cookies to evaluate user responses to new advertisements, pages, or features.</li>
                                                                <li>Functionality or Preference Cookies - While you're browsing the Websites, cookies are utilized to retain information you've inputted or choices you've made (like your username, language, or region) on the Websites. They also store your preferences when customizing the Websites to enhance your Desi Rishta experience. These preferences are retained through the use of persistent cookies, so the next time you visit the Websites, you won't need to set them again.</li>
                                                                <li>Targeting Advertising Cookies - These cookies are set by third-party advertising platforms or networks, or by Desi Rishta itself, to deliver advertisements and monitor ad performance. They enable advertising networks to display ads that may be of interest to you based on your activities (commonly referred to as "behavioural," "tracking," or "targeted" advertising) on the Websites. Subsequently, these platforms may utilize information about your visit to target you with advertising that aligns with your interests, both on the Desi Rishta Websites and on other websites. For instance, these cookies retain information about which browsers have visited the Websites.</li>
                                                            </ul>
                                                            <p class="mb-2 mt-4"><b>5. When does Desi Rishta set cookies?</b></p>
                                                            <p class="mb-2"> We utilize cookies across our websites, mobile sites, and mobile applications. Any browser accessing these sites will receive cookies from us, facilitating quicker identification upon your return. Cookies aid in discerning which pages or information you find most valuable or engaging on our websites.</p>
                                                            <p class="mb-2">Desi Rishta may also employ certain cookies for its own analytics purposes, distinct from Google Analytics, Facebook Pixel. These cookies assist in generating statistics and reports concerning visitors and their interactions on the website or app.</p>

                                                            <p class="mb-2 mt-4"><b>6. How are cookies utilized for the purpose of online analytics?</b></p>
                                                            <p class="mb-2">On Desi Rishta, we may utilize web analytics services like Google Analytics, Facebook Pixel. These services assist us in analysing user interactions with the services, which may include tracking the third-party websites users arrive from. The data collected by these technologies may be shared with or collected directly by the service providers, who utilize it to assess your utilization of the services. Additionally, we employ Google Analytics, Facebook Pixel for specific purposes related to online marketing, as outlined in the subsequent sections.</p>

                                                            <p class="mb-2 mt-4"><b>7. How are cookies employed for advertising objectives?</b></p>
                                                            <p class="mb-2">Cookies and other advertising technologies, like beacons, pixels, and tags, aid us in delivering pertinent ads to you with greater precision. They also facilitate aggregated auditing, research, and reporting for advertisers, and help us improve our service while determining when content has been presented to you. Collaborating with website analytics and advertising partners such as Google and Facebook, Instagram, X, Linkedin, Youtube and other online platforms, we showcase Desi Rishta ads on third-party publisher websites. These partners may deploy cookies on your computer's web browser, enabling them to recognize your device. This recognition allows the ad server to display Desi Rishta ads elsewhere online and enables our analytics software to assess your engagement and interactions with Desi Rishta services. Consequently, ad servers can compile anonymous, de-identified data regarding the viewing of our ads, interactions with them, and subsequent visits to Desi Rishta websites and applications. This data empowers ad networks to deliver targeted advertisements they believe will interest you the most, and it allows us to optimize the performance of our advertising campaigns and website usability. In summary, we leverage analytics data in conjunction with information about online ads displayed through platforms like the Google and Facebook, Instagram, X, Linkedin, Youtube and other online platforms for Advertisers to understand how anonymous users engage with our website after encountering our ads.</p>


                                                            <p class="mb-2 mt-4" id="sec8"><b>8. Which third-party cookies does Desi Rishta employ?</b></p>
                                                            <p class="mb-2">Please be aware that third parties, such as advertising networks and providers of external services like web traffic analysis services, may also utilize cookies on our Services. Additionally, note that the names of cookies, pixels, and other technologies may change over time.</p>
                                                            <p class="mb-2"> We collaborate with trusted partners to assist us in delivering advertising, and they may place cookies on your device. Furthermore, we integrate content from social networks into our pages, such as embedded Facebook feeds. These social networks, including Google, Facebook, Instagram, X, Linkedin, Youtube and other online platforms, may also set cookies on your device. If a user logs into Facebook, Twitter, or Google+ via our website, a cookie will be stored on the user's computer, mirroring the process when logging into these social networks directly.</p>
                                                            <p class="mb-2">Moreover, we utilize Google Analytics and Pixel on our Services to analyse user interactions. Google Analytics and Pixel employs performance cookies to monitor customer interactions. For example, using cookies, Google and Facebook can inform us about which pages our users view, which are the most popular, the time of day our websites are visited, whether visitors have visited our websites previously, the website that referred the visitor to our websites, and similar information. All of this data is anonymized.</p>
                                                            <p class="mb-2">We recommend reviewing the respective privacy policies of these external services to gain an understanding of the data these organizations hold about you and how they process it.</p>
                                                            <p class="mb-2"> For reference, here are the privacy policies of some external services:</p>
                                                            <ul>
                                                                <li>Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/policy.php</li>
                                                                <li>AdSense: https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads</li>
                                                                <li>Google Analytics: http://www.google.com/analytics/learn/privacy.html</li>
                                                                <li>Google Tag Manager: https://www.google.com/analytics/tag-manager/faq/</li>
                                                                <li>Google DoubleClick: https://support.google.com/dfp_premium/answer/2839090?hl=en</li>
                                                            </ul>

                                                            <p class="mb-2 mt-4"><b>9. What do Web Beacons refer to?</b></p>
                                                            <p class="mb-2"> Desi Rishta occasionally promotes its services on third-party websites. To assess the effectiveness of our advertising campaigns, we may utilize visitor identification technologies like "web beacons" or "action tags." These technologies track visitors who have visited our site after encountering a Desi Rishta banner ad on a third-party site.</p>
                                                            <p class="mb-2"> By browsing our site, you consent to the placement of cookies and web beacons on your computer or device. If you wish to avoid receiving web beacons, you can either discontinue using our site or adjust your browsing settings accordingly.</p>


                                                            <p class="mb-2 mt-4"><b>10. How can you manage cookies?</b></p>
                                                            <p class="mb-2"> Most web browsers offer options to control cookies through their settings preferences. However, disabling these cookies does not mean you won't see any internet advertising; rather, the ads you encounter may not be tailored to your interests. It's important to note that turning off third-party cookies listed in our policy's preceding sections <a href="#sec8" class="faqlink-text">(section 8)</a> may not completely eliminate tailored advertisements and recommendations, as the list is subject to change.</p>
                                                            <p class="mb-2"> You have several options for managing cookie settings on your devices, though essential cookies cannot be disabled. Disabling certain cookies may render parts of a website inaccessible or compromise its performance, features, or services.</p>
                                                            <p class="mb-2"> You can adjust cookie settings through the privacy settings of your web browser. Keep in mind that blocking all cookies using browser settings may restrict access to portions of our website or others'. For guidance on changing cookie settings, consult the 'options' or 'preferences' menu of your internet browser. Alternatively, utilize the 'Help' feature in your browser for more detailed instructions.</p>
                                                            <p class="mb-2"> Here are some helpful links for understanding cookie settings in popular browsers:</p>
